{{gherdëina}}[[File:Weizenähren.jpg|thumb|L selin]]L '''selin''' (''Triticum aestivum'')  ([[Ladin gherdëina|gherdëina]]: ''selin'', [[badiot]]: ''selin'' o ''formënt'', [[Ladin fascian|fascian]]: ''forment'') ie na sort de [[blava]].<br>
L selin ie un di [[cuncier]]es plu mpurtanc al mond. Tl 2017 ovun sëura dut l mond prodot 772 milions de [[tona|tones]] de selin sun 220.4 millions de hectar de ciamps. <ref>https://www.fao.org/worldfoodsituation/csdb/en/ Roma, Talia: Nazions Unides, Food and Agriculture Organization. 10 merz 2019.</ref>

